Hope this email find you well. This is Shuman from Kyearn Architecture.

Recently we had a project located at 32 Flinders avenue, St Ives with concrete roof. We would like to invite you to provide a fee proposal for mechanical and electrical services for design and documentation. Please review the attached PDF for DA approved architectural set.

Please do not hesitate to contact me if you need more information for this project. Look forward to receiving your fee proposal soon.
